COOK: Skilled food preparation

Category: Domestic
Base skill: 35% (+5%/level, cap 98%)

Preparing food well: not just making it edible, but making it good,
and getting the most out of whatever ingredients are on hand. A
professional-grade version of basic camp cooking.

NOTES:
  No AetherMUD command currently rolls this skill directly. It is
  available for character concept and staff-adjudicated roleplay.

